Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.06,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,È colpa tua!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:48.81,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.36,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutto questo non sarebbe mai successo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,se non lo avessi sposato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avanti, di' qualcosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.74,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsè, per te è solo un bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:59.03,sign_4472_24_Hatamoto_Akie,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,370)\p1\fscx600\fscy600\c&HD04E32&\1a&H7C&\blur1.3\move(170,227,121,227)\clip(66,124.667,462,348)}m -1 3 l 21 3 l 21 9 l -1 9
